{
  "chapter": 55,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述了芮玮与叶青被困海底洞穴数日后，终于发现通往外界的光线。两人沿着激流前行，险些被旋涡吞噬，最终找到安全出口。芮玮为叶青取回衣物，两人修补衣衫，关系愈发亲密。洞穴地面刻有“无名氏坐化”五字，暗示曾有高人在此坐化，为后续剧情埋下伏笔。全章以二人情感发展为主，穿插探险与发现，节奏舒缓而温情。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "她们久不见咱们上去，早以为咱们死去，不会有人再关心！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "咱们顺着这激流走走看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "摔痛了吗？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，好难走呀，咱们就在这里住下去好啦。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "傻孩子，长住此地不是办法，来，我抱你走。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，大哥……我……",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "青儿，咱们得救了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊哟",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "你等着，我去拿衣服。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "你在摸什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "穿好衣服，咱们吃鱼。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "笑什么，来、吃鱼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "这种鱼生在漆黑不见光线的泉底里，难怪眼睛这么小，其实眼睛对它们毫无用处。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "你放心，现在再吃鱼，无论如何不会再对你无礼。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "青儿，你生什么气？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你还好意思说，不想那几天你对我好凶。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "我怎么凶啦？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不来了，不来了，你有意羞我。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "打重点嘛。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "你忍心打吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我……我……不忍心打……",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "咱们快想法上去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "咱们这样子怎么上去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "上去不会有人了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "假若有人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "那就不好意思了，给她们看到咱们衣不蔽体，当真要令人无地自容。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我来补。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "青儿，咱们关系不同，你还怕羞什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "你刚才在地上摸什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "地上有字。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无名氏坐化，那……那无名老人果然住在这岛上！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    }
  ],
